    <title><![CDATA[树莓派安装bypy百度云python客户端]]></title>
    <link href="http://wutill.com/2015/07/16/bypy/"/>
    <id>http://wutill.com/2015/07/16/bypy/</id>
    <published>2015-07-16T09:06:36.000Z</published>
    <updated>2015-07-17T01:20:27.000Z</updated>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="前因">前因</h2>
<p>  树莓派作为移动小系统，IP经常来回变动，每次扫描其MAC地址，也可以得到IP，但是我想用<br>Python写得百度客户端，每次开机启动把IP同步到百度云上，作为一个尝试。<br><a href="https://github.com/houtianze/bypy" target="_blank" rel="external">百度云Python客户端</a></p>
<h2 id="代码">代码</h2>
<figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">IP=`ifconfig|grep "inet " | cut -d: -f2 | awk '{print $1}' | grep -v "^127."` </div><div class="line">echo "" &gt;/data/ip/$IP.txt</div><div class="line">/usr/bin/python  /data/bypy/bypy.py upload /data/ip/  &gt;&gt;/tmp/test    </div><div class="line">以上代码加到 /etc/rc.local exit 0前面</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="问题">问题</h2>
<p>怎么就不通过，最后发现报错</p>
<figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div><div class="line">20</div><div class="line">21</div><div class="line">22</div><div class="line">23</div><div class="line">24</div><div class="line">25</div><div class="line">26</div><div class="line">27</div><div class="line">28</div><div class="line">29</div><div class="line">30</div><div class="line">31</div><div class="line">32</div><div class="line">33</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">*WARNING*: Cannot detect the system encoding, assume it's 'UTF-8'</div><div class="line">Token file: '//.bypy/bypy.json'</div><div class="line">Hash Cache file: '//.bypy/bypy.pickle'</div><div class="line">App root path at Baidu Yun '/apps/bypy'</div><div class="line">sys.stdin.encoding = None</div><div class="line">sys.stdout.encoding = None</div><div class="line">sys.stderr.encoding = ANSI_X3.4-1968</div><div class="line">----</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">&lt;E&gt; [13:13:52] Error while loading baidu pcs token:</div><div class="line">&lt;E&gt; [13:13:52] Traceback (most recent call last):</div><div class="line">  File "/data/bypy/bypy.py", line 1480, in __load_local_json</div><div class="line">    with open(TokenFilePath, 'rb') as infile:</div><div class="line">IOError: [Errno 2] No such file or directory: u'//.bypy/bypy.json'</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">Please visit:</div><div class="line">https://openapi.baidu.com/oauth/2.0/authorize?scope=basic+netdisk&amp;redirect_uri=oob&amp;response_type=code&amp;client_id=q8WE4EpCsau1oS</div><div class="line">And authorize this app</div><div class="line">Paste the Authorization Code here within 10 minutes.</div><div class="line">Press [Enter] when you are done</div><div class="line">&lt;E&gt; [13:13:52] Exception occurred:</div><div class="line">Traceback (most recent call last):</div><div class="line">  File "/data/bypy/bypy.py", line 3421, in main</div><div class="line">    verbose = args.verbose, debug = args.debug)</div><div class="line">  File "/data/bypy/bypy.py", line 1172, in __init__</div><div class="line">    result = self.__auth()</div><div class="line">  File "/data/bypy/bypy.py", line 1592, in __auth</div><div class="line">    return self.__server_auth()</div><div class="line">  File "/data/bypy/bypy.py", line 1556, in __server_auth</div><div class="line">    auth_code = ask(msg).strip()</div><div class="line">  File "/data/bypy/bypy.py", line 363, in askc</div><div class="line">    return raw_input()</div><div class="line">EOFError: EOF when reading a line</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="解决">解决</h2>
<figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">TokenFilePath = ConfigDir + os.sep + 'bypy.json'</div><div class="line">HashCachePath = ConfigDir + os.sep + 'bypy.pickle'</div><div class="line">改为</div><div class="line">TokenFilePath = '/root/.bypy/bypy.json'</div><div class="line">HashCachePath = '/root/.bypy/bypy.pickle'</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>    ]]></content>
