<figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">删除右边错误的标签</div><div class="line">保险起见 删除db.json 删除 source下 tags下的相应标签</div><div class="line">多个标签 [<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="number">2</span>,<span class="number">3.</span>...]</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">hexo2<span class="number">.83</span> 用<span class="number">3.0</span>有问题</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

